<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jennifer Garner wants you to vote.</p>

<p>The 48-year-old actress made sure to spread awareness for Voter Registration Day on Tuesday by wearing a bright red sweater which had 'vote vote vote' emblazoned across it.</p>

<p>She teamed the top with a pair of clinging navy leggings and black Brooks running shoes and a blue face mask.</p>

<p>Her brunette tresses were pulled back in a ponytail as she let her natural looks shine by going make-up free. </p>

