<p>Last month an In Touch Weekly source claimed Jennifer and her businessman beau John Miller 'are no longer together' after a less than two-year romance. </p>

<p>The insider said they 'split up before L.A. went into lockdown,' adding that they 'remain on friendly terms so there’s a possibility that they could rekindle their relationship in the future, but right now it’s over.'</p>

<p>DailyMail.com contacted Jennifer's rep for comment on the matter.</p>

